Pick up the plunger on the ground.

Put the plunger in the left cabinet under the sink on the right.

pick up the red plunger right of the toilet from the floor
turn to the right twice go to the shower curtain and turn to the right and go to the front of the right sink cabinet doors

high_descs: Move forward towards the bathtub then turn left and face the black towel on the wall in between the toilet and the bathtub.
Pick up the red plunger from the floor between the toilet and the toilet brush.
Turn around and move towards the turquoise door then right and move to the sink closest to the toilet.
Open the vanity cabinet door underneath the left side of the sink, place the plunger to the right of the candlestick, and then close the cabinet door.
